awards.title: Dean's List
awards.summary: Awarded to students who have a cumulative GPA of 3.8 or higher.

awards.title: Transfer Merit Scholarship
awards.summary: Awarded to UH System Community College students that plan on transferring to UH Manoa who have a minimum GPA of 3.3 and at least 24 transferable credits. The scholarship is worth $2,000/year.

awards.title: 2nd Place Coded Solution
awards.summary: Was a part of Team DarkMode and got awarded $2,000. Created a web application that has an A.I. chatbot assistant which allow users to ask questions relating to UH ITS.
